   "service": "networking/firewall",
   "enabled": true,
   "_note": "composed by regression/scenarios/composer.py — targets: firewall, firewall-rule | adopt stamps stripped on purpose: the firewall lookup (GET /v1/firewalls?vpc_name=regrvpc{unique}&product_type=IGW) only resolves against a self-created VPC, and IGW is 1:1 per VPC — must not collide with the session-shared VPC's IGW.",
   "steps": [
